Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for re-submission
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to next 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to be followed by 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for all instances of 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' within a case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Time until 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' from the start of the case
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' before any re-submission or approval action
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Request Payment' in cases where the declaration is eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' to be followed by any approval activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Time of 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' cycle within the entire process flow
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases that require director approval
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration APPROVED by DIRECTOR occurs

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' compared to cases without it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION does not occur
